text: Victorville is a city in San Bernardino County, California. It is on the Interstate 15 between San Bernardino and Barstow. At the 2020 census, 134,810 people lived there. The city was incorporated in 1962. ==References== Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in San Bernardino County, California Category:1962 establishments in California
